Get R Releases

Source: R/plot_r_releases.R
get_r_releases.Rd

Get R Releases

get_r_releases(releases = rversions::r_versions(dots = TRUE))

Arguments

releases

R releases as retrieved by r_versions, (default: rversions::r_versions(dots = TRUE))

Value

data frame with R releases

Examples

releases <- get_r_releases()
#> Warning: Expected 3 pieces. Missing pieces filled with `NA` in 13 rows [1, 2, 6, 11, 15, 18, 20, 22, 23, 25, 27, 31, 33].
head(releases)
